    <p class="section-label">Phase 2</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">30+ interviews, 6 expert conversations, and 80+ ideation participants</h2>
    <div class="case-body">
      <p>Phase 2 was designed to move from the broad problem space and strategic framework established in Phase 1 into concrete, scored, and prioritized solution concepts. The team engaged in deep research — 30+ clinician interviews across AHN and partner organizations, 30+ customer interviews and concept tests, 6 conversations with external experts including Forrester analysts, startups, and national advocacy groups, and 6 collaborative ideation sessions with 80+ cross-enterprise and external participants.</p>
      <p>Starting from six prioritized opportunity areas, the team generated 12 solution concepts, scored each against impact, difficulty, and scalability, and narrowed to the five highest-potential concepts to present for leadership alignment and funding approval.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

