    <p class="section-label">Foundational Concept</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">The BH Care Hub as a platform, not a product</h2>
    <div class="case-body">
      <p>The cornerstone of the solution concepts is the BH Hub — a consolidation and curation point for behavioral health solutions, built on the Living Health Platform and integrated seamlessly into the broader customer and clinician experience. The design intent was explicit: this is not a standalone app.</p>
      <p>The BH Hub isn't the Highmark app. It isn't Highmark.com or MyStrength or the EMR or Virtual Care. It connects and integrates with all of these to create a single, simple access point for people seeking BH care and resources — and a launching point for the four other concepts to plug into.</p>
    </div>
